name: Open918
tagline: A library to decode UIC 918.2 encoded barcodes
body:
### Welcome to Open918
Open918 is a project to create a library to parse, validate and handle barcodes by the UIC 918.x standards. 

### Authors and Contributors
* @joelhaasnoot
* BliksemLabs
